text: Ishimbayevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Ishimbayevsky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 463 as of 2010. There are 8 streets. == Geography == It is located 38 km from Maloyaz. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Ishimbayevo
